Download this version of World Chef to enjoy exclusive decorations, costumes, and lots of Halloween surprises!

A new version of World Chef has arrived and it’s full of good news!

- Hiring a chef will no longer compromise your expansion plans, because from now on, you’ll be able to expand with items you can get from happy customers and from crates!

- Twenty-five new expansion slots are available now. Make your restaurant huge!

- VIPs become humbler and they stop the pressure on leveled-up dishes!

- The World Chef Factory keeps working on improvements and polishing for you.

New version of World Chef! Here's what's on the menu:

- The Billboard Guy now brings you videos and something else! You can also complete tasks from external companies and get Gems and other valuable rewards!

- The Chillout Area is back to its old rewards, as requested by our dear chefs! Get Basic Crates for catering Birthdays and Weddings and Deluxe Crates for catering Pool Parties!

Roll out that red carpet and welcome the new chefs!

- We’ve been scouting the best chefs around the world and we’re happy to introduce you to a new Snack chef, a new Hipster chef, and a new Premium Grill chef! They’re excited and ready to spice things up!

- All iPhone X users can rejoice because World Chef has support for iPhone X!

Roll out that red carpet and welcome the new chefs!

- We’ve been scouting the best chefs around the world and we’re happy to introduce you to a new Snack chef, a new Hipster chef, and a new Premium Grill chef! They’re excited and ready to spice things up!

- All iPhone X users can rejoice because World Chef has support for iPhone X!

Ladies and gentlemen, drumroll please… announcing lots of new things for your restaurant!

- We’ve convinced more of the world’s best chefs to come and join your restaurant. Introducing a new Australian chef, a new Carnival chef, and a new Fusion chef.

- What goes around comes around. Keep serving mouthwatering food to tables for the chance to get gem tips in your new tip jar.

Because all chefs love a good, clean kitchen we’ve done some polishing to keep everything in tip-top shape!

Because your customers live very busy lives, it’s time to show ‘em what your chefs are made of!

- We’ve also done some polishing to make sure your customers are as happy as they can be.

- Check out the new Halloween Event! Collect Vampire stakes to get the new Vampire Bartender and spooky decorations.
